ata-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bop1665702962040.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bop1665702962040.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bop1665702962040.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bop1665702962040\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Support for Unicode in PGS Connector\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface PGS connector for PostgreSQL supports the full Unicode range.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bop1665702962040__p_d58109e1_d58110e1_d58111e1\">To enable Unicode support in the connector, set the assignment setting <code class=\"ph codeph\">$DEF_CHARSET=</code>UTF8. This ensures that the Uniface C packing code is mapped to W packing code. This enables Unicode characters to be used in table names and column names, in the SQL Workbench, and with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sql</span> ProcScript statement.</p>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"bop1665702962040__note_w3698ab1b5b3_w3699ab1b5_w3700ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> For PostgreSQL, you must ensure that the\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">$DEF_CHARSET=</code>UTF8 is set for all applications that access the data via the\n         PGS connector. If it is set to different character sets, it can corrupt the data.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bop1665702962040__p_d58112e1_d58113e1_d58114e1\">When modeling application data, use wide-character\n         packing codes (such as W20) for fields. W packing codes are stored as UTF-8 and support the\n         full Unicode range. By default, Unicode support for W packing codes is limited to\n         characters in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). You can enable storage of the entire\n         Unicode range (Supplementary Multilingual Planes) by setting the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">smp</span>\n         connector option. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"msy1665702733836.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msy1665702733836.html\" title=\"Include the entire Unicode range (SMP)\">smp</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bop1665702962040__p_d58115e1_d58116e1_d58117e1\">For or more information, consult the PostgreSQL documentation.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526161\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526161\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Support for Unicode in PGS Connector Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Support for Unicode in PGS Connector The Uniface PGS connector for PostgreSQL supports the full Unicode range. To enable Unicode support in the connector, set the assignment setting $DEF_CHARSET= UTF8. This ensures that the Uniface C packing code is mapped to W packing code. This enables Unicode characters to be used in table names and column names, in the SQL Workbench, and with the sql ProcScript statement. Important: For PostgreSQL, you must ensure that the $DEF_CHARSET= UTF8 is set for all applications that access the data via the PGS connector. If it is set to different character sets, it can corrupt the data. When modeling application data, use wide-character packing codes (such as W20) for fields. W packing codes are stored as UTF-8 and support the full Unicode range. By default, Unicode support for W packing codes is limited to characters in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). You can enable storage of the entire Unicode range (Supplementary Multilingual Planes) by setting the smp connector option. For more information, see smp . For or more information, consult the PostgreSQL documentation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}